title: Grateful Dead Live at The Spectrum on 1988-09-11
description:
Set 1

Iko Iko, Feel Like A Stranger-> Franklin's Tower, Little Red Rooster, Peggy-O, Memphis Blues, Tennessee Jed, Promised Land

Set 2

Foolish Heart, Victim Or The Crime, Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain-> Drums-> Space-> The Wheel-> Stella Blue-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: It's All Over Now Baby Blue
